name: TrumpCoin
description: What is TrumpCoin(DTC)? TrumpCoin (DTC) launched in 11/5/2023 by a team based in United Kingdom and it is a meme cryptocurrency project that is rewarding its holders. TrumpCoin (DTC) is also a community made and owned project with 5% USDT rewards for all holders. The team of TrumpCoin is committed to building a strong and supportive community that shares the vision of making meme coins great again. They are dedicated to transparency and fairness, and always looking for ways to improve and innovate.
